description: A brash young reporter discovers he has powers that will change the destiny of the world in a thrilling, futuristic miniseries! The mystery over the global organization code-named Sci-Tech explodes this issue! Ace science reporter Leo Lomax is thrust into the middle of an all-out war between Sci-Tech gunmen and Ninja Metamorphs. As Leo gets more involved, he discovers that he has secret super-powers himself...and now both the Sci-Tech agents and the Naturalists want to capture and study him...dead or alive!
name: The Deep Blue Sea

description: The global war between the super scientific agency known as Sci-Tech and the stealth-warrior Naturalists reaches skyward! Young Leo Lomax must don a rocket pack and join the Sci-Tech Air Rangers to rescue a friend from the murderous clutches of a shape-shifting Harpy! The result is mayhem over San Francisco, as a deadly aerial duel erupts! Plus: The shocking secret history of Sci-Tech finally is revealed; and the debut of the bright, beautiful silicon-chip woman called Omnia, whose connection to Leo will shock you!
name: Heaven and Earth
